title: 请问怎么在ChestCommands菜单插件内打开其他GUI插件的界面
author: xu1072181422
txt_content:
请问怎么在ChestCommands菜单插件内打开其他GUI插件的界面

现在的情况是打开后很快就消失请问应该怎么设置

replies.author: Animalworld
replies.txt_content:
TreeDiagramA3:
  NAME: "&e\u6302\u673A"
  LORE:
    - "&7\u5DE6\u952E\u70B9\u51FB"
  ID: 384
  KEEP-OPEN: true
  COMMAND: "op:chestcommands open \u804C\u4E1A"
  POSITION-X: 3
  POSITION-Y: 1

在里面填入一个KEEP-OPEN: true
